{"tid":1034174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［團聚唔係大哂］一圖睇哂美國的家庭團聚條件","createTime":"2019-02-23T16:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T17:34:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f21d6e4b76725f952240f58c55d3f7045869ee9","tid":1034174,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hnyPDx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hnyPDx.png&h=4bd99d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尋日我哋提出咗短期內具體可行，港府可自行立法解決，不需中央同意嘅單程證改革建議（<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/2295399540499766/?type=3&amp;theater），其實都係參考美國現行相關政策。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F2295399540499766%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E5%85%B6%E5%AF%A6%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E5%8F%83%E8%80%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%8F%BE%E8%A1%8C%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E3%80%82&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=04f9c70a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/2295399540499766/?type=3&amp;theater），其實都係參考美國現行相關政策。</a><br />\n<br />\n係呀，即使喺重視人權嘅美國，家庭團聚都唔係大X晒㗎，一樣要符合一啲基本條件。最核心嘅價值觀係，你唔好諗住同一個美國人結咗婚，美國政府就老奉咁有責任去養你，任得你又食又拎囉。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<br />\n我的削減單程證建議－梁啟智<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2589%258A%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=48465e1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%2589%258A%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2596%25AE%25E7%25A8%258B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%2F&h=cd18759e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%89%8A%E6%B8%9B%E5%96%AE%E7%A8%8B%E8%AD%89%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/907020282671039/posts/2296910337015353/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F907020282671039%2Fposts%2F2296910337015353%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3aaa4cb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/907020282671039/posts/2296910337015353/</a>"},{"pid":"b1bcacad27620d33a49371f34e0c454e542fe3c6","tid":1034174,"uid":146092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:48:52.000Z","msg":"你知，我知，個個都知，咁又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61e4c16201136c97668eb6e738d855a94d7ec560","tid":1034174,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rhbLFMa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrhbLFMa.png&h=cfd18830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#請用數據來說服我<br />\n<br />\n問：有協助新移民嘅組織表示：「新移民參與勞動比率跟香港人相若，對社會有貢獻」，係唔係真㗎？ <br />\n<br />\n答：這說法相當誤導。以年齡細分的話，整體香港人的勞動比率只在 55+ 的組別明顯降低，這是因為他們已經為香港勞碌了半生，從工作崗位退下來，享受退休生活。<br />\n<br />\n相反，在 25 - 44 歲的壯年人仕組別，新移民的勞動參與率遠低於香港人。香港人在 55 歲以後才能享受的退休生活，他們早已經擁有。<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n民政事務署 - 內地新來港人仕的統計數字<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/public_services/services_for_new_arrivals_from_the_mainland/surveys.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_services%2Fservices_for_new_arrivals_from_the_mainland%2Fsurveys.htm&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9efec4b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/public_services/services_for_new_arrivals_from_the_mainland/surveys.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港2016年中期人口統計 - 主題性報告：內地來港定居未足七年人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp459_tc.jsp?productCode=B1120101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp459_tc.jsp%3FproductCode%3DB1120101&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=56f2a3be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp459_tc.jsp?productCode=B1120101</a>"},{"pid":"0593446a98d76484a268ae7e154a8b92a916733e","tid":1034174,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDy97rv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDy97rv.png&h=c350025f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#請用數據來說服我<br />\n<br />\n問：有協助新移民嘅組織表示：「定居本港的新移民都是年輕力壯的一群」，因此醫療需求較低，係唔係真㗎？<br />\n<br />\n答：首先呢，雖然新移民嘅年齡中位數的確係比香港人低，但咁唔代表新移民醫療需求比較低，因為年齡中位數並唔係咁用的。<br />\n<br />\n新移民的年齡中位數為 34 歲，只代表了一半的新移民年齡高於 34 歲，另一半則低於，如此而已。但 35 歲是高於 34 歲，100 歲也是高於 34 歲，這差別在年齡中位數看不出來。<br />\n<br />\n比較有用的數字，要看年紀比較大的新移民的絕對人數。2017 年來港的新移民當中， 23.8%（多於一萬人）屬 45 歲或以上，2.4%（多於一千人）屬 65 歲或以上，對當前已水深火熱的公營醫療所帶來的壓力，絕對不容忽視。<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n民政事務署 - 內地新來港人仕的統計數字<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/public_services/services_for_new_arrivals_from_the_mainland/surveys.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic_services%2Fservices_for_new_arrivals_from_the_mainland%2Fsurveys.htm&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=9efec4b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/public_services/services_for_new_arrivals_from_the_mainland/surveys.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港2016年中期人口統計 - 主題性報告：內地來港定居未足七年人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp459_tc.jsp?productCode=B1120101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp459_tc.jsp%3FproductCode%3DB1120101&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xaf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=56f2a3be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp459_tc.jsp?productCode=B1120101</a>"},{"pid":"0d82428ea23283cedbe9267615e6409c78d1ef4c","tid":1034174,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"社區組織呢？<br />\n去咗邊？<br />\n有冇人見到佢哋？"},{"pid":"fae960f531b01eaeba908bcea4e64603582e46f6","tid":1034174,"uid":179192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:32:56.000Z","msg":"有冇靚女想黎美國同我團聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608a886598656c7721ada2b6800c2df7c090e21e","tid":1034174,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d82428ea23283cedbe9267615e6409c78d1ef4c","tid":1034174,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"社區組織呢？<br />\n去咗邊？<br />\n有冇人見到佢哋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"滅左族, 搵聯合國介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}